title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Wood & Related Articles
description: Imports of Intra EU - Wood & Related Articles in the United Kingdom increased to 369.03 GBP Million in September from 364.09 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Wood & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 182.92 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 522.79 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 73.88 GBP Million in December of 1996. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Wood & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
